{"ID":"20260214225220-6tab0f8","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260214225220-6tab0f8","title":"偏导数","type":"doc","updated":"20260215132349"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260215132225-iq8u753","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260215132225-iq8u753","updated":"20260215132349"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2026-02-15 13:22:34"}]},{"ID":"20260214225220-a4hebkw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260214225220-a4hebkw","updated":"20260215132143"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对于二元函数 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":" z = f(x,y)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 而言，z 对 x 的偏导数是，当 x 产生微小变动时，z 的变动量除以 x 的变动量。\n某点处的 x 的偏导数的几何意义：沿 x 轴方向的切线的斜率"}]},{"ID":"20260215132349-1s15p27","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260215132349-1s15p27","updated":"20260215132349"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260215132349-q3aii5y","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260215132349-q3aii5y","updated":"20260215132349"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260215132143-oabgh3m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260215132143-oabgh3m","updated":"20260215132612"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题型1：\n求具体点处的偏导数"}]}]},{"ID":"20260215132620-06fdum8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260215132620-06fdum8","updated":"20260215132620"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260215132620-h69j68d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260215132620-h69j68d","updated":"20260215132648"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题型 2：\n复合函数的偏导数"}]}]},{"ID":"20260215132648-h9cfotx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260215132648-h9cfotx","updated":"20260215132648"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260215132648-8y0o9m0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260215132648-8y0o9m0","updated":"20260215133012"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题型 3：\n隐函数求